# INVITES BACKEND DEVELOPMENT

The invites backend was initially created as a hobby project to create invitations to events.

Uses Node.js for the server-side programming with the following technical features:

* JWT For Authentication
* Cloudinary for Image Storage
* Mongo db for Users control
* Mysql as main DB
* Zod for model validations
* bcryptjs for encryptions
* socket.io for web sockets connections

## Installation

Use the package manager [npm](https://docs.npmjs.com/cli/v10/configuring-npm/install) to install the dependencies.

```bash
npm install
```

To build the typescript project run

```bash
npm run build
```

To run the project

```bash
npm start
```
